{:name=>"456", :status=>"PLANNED WORK", :date=>"02/22/2015 12:53PM", :text=>"\r\n                    <span class=\"TitlePlannedWork\" >Planned Work</span>\r\n                    \r\n                  <a class=\"plannedWorkDetailLink\" onclick=ShowHide(88837);>\r\n[6] Brooklyn Bridge-bound trains run express from Parkchester to Hunts Point Av\r\n</a><div id= 88837 class=\"plannedWorkDetail\" >Weekends, 6:45 AM Sat to 7 PM Sun, until Mar 1\r\n\r\nFor service to St Lawrence Av, Morrison Av-Soundview, Elder and Whitlock Avs,\r\ntake the [6] to Hunts Point Av and transfer to a Pelham Bay Park-bound [6].\r\n\r\nFor service from these stations, take the [6] to Parkchester and transfer to a\r\nBrooklyn Bridge-bound [6].\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n                \r\n              \r\n                    <span class=\"TitlePlannedWork\" >Planned Work</span>\r\n                    \r\n                  <a class=\"plannedWorkDetailLink\" onclick=ShowHide(89879);>\r\n[5] No trains between Grand Central-42 St and Bowling Green\r\n</a><div id= 89879 class=\"plannedWorkDetail\" >[4] [6] and [R] trains provide alternate service\r\n<a href=http://advisory.mtanyct.info/pdf_files/ServiceGuide.pdf target=_blank>Weekend</a>, Saturday and Sunday, Feb 21 - 22\r\n\r\n[5] service operates every 20 minutes between Dyre Av and Grand Central-42 St.\r\n  &#149;  Downtown trains make local stops from 125 St to Grand Central-42 St.\r\n\r\n<table class=plannedworkTableStyle  width=80%><tr><td>Travel Alternatives<td align=right>[TP]</table>\r\n\r\nFor 14 St-Union Sq and Brooklyn Bridge, take the [4] [6].\r\n\r\nFor Fulton St, Wall St and Bowling Green, use nearby [R] stations at\r\nCortlandt St, Rector St and Whitehall St.\r\n\r\n&#149; Transfer between [5] and [R] trains at 59 St.\r\n&#149; Transfer between [5] and [4] [6] trains at Grand Central-42 St.\r\n&#149; Transfer between [4] [6] and [R] trains at Canal St.\r\n\r\nNote: No [4] service between Brooklyn Bridge and New Lots Av.\r\n\r\n<table class=plannedworkTableStyle  border=1 cellspacing=1 cellpadding=5 rules=none frame=box><td>&nbsp;&nbsp;[ad]&nbsp;&nbsp;<td>This service change affects one or more ADA accessible stations. Please call 511 for help with planningyour trip. If you are deaf or hard of hearing, use your preferred relay service provider or the free 711 relay.&nbsp;&nbsp;</table>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n                \r\n              \r\n                    <span class=\"TitlePlannedWork\" >Planned Work</span>\r\n                    \r\n                  <a class=\"plannedWorkDetailLink\" onclick=ShowHide(89877);>\r\n[4] No trains between Brooklyn Bridge and New Lots Av<br clear=left>[2] [3] [D] [N] [Q] [R] trains provide alternate service\r\n</a><div id= 89877 class=\"plannedWorkDetail\" >Weekends, 11:45 PM Fri to 5 AM Mon, Feb 20 - 23  &#149;  Feb 27 - Mar 2\r\n\r\n[4] service operates between Woodlawn and Brooklyn Bridge, making local stops.\r\n\r\nLate Night [3] service is extended to New Lots Av.\r\n\r\n<table class=plannedworkTableStyle  width=80%><tr><td>Travel Alternatives<td align=right>[TP]</table>\r\nFor service between Manhattan and Brooklyn, take the [D] or [Q].\r\n\r\nFor Lower Manhattan and Downtown Brooklyn, take the [2] [3] or [N] [R].\r\n\r\nFor service between Borough Hall and Franklin Av, take the [2] [3].\r\nTake the [3] between Franklin Av and New Lots Av.\r\n\r\n<table class=plannedworkTableStyle  width=75% border=1 cellspacing=1 cellpadding=3 rules=rows frame=hsides><tr><td bgcolor=#FAF8CC>[4] Station<td bgcolor=#FAF8CC>Nearby [R] Station  <td bgcolor=#FAF8CC>Nearby [2] [3] Station<tr><td>Brooklyn Bridge&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<td>City Hall<td>Park Place<tr><td>Fulton St [ad] <td>Cortlandt St [ad] <td>Fulton St [ad]<tr><td>Wall St<td>Rector St<td>Wall St<tr><td>Bowling Green [ad]<td>Whitehall St-South Ferry  [1]<td>&nbsp;&nbsp;&mdash;<tr><td>Borough Hall<td>Court St orJay St-MetroTech  [ad]  [A] [C] [F]&nbsp;<td>Borough Hall  [ad]<tr><td>Nevins St<td>DeKalb Av  [ad]  [Q]<td>Nevins St</table>\r\n<table class=plannedworkTableStyle  width=75% cellpadding=3 rules=rows frame=hsides><tr bgcolor=000000><td colspan=2>Key Transfer Stations<tr><td>Bleecker St/B'way-Lafayette St  [ad]<td>[4] and [D] [F]<tr><td>14 St-Union Sq  [ad]  or Canal St<td>[4] and [N] [Q] [R]<tr><td>Atlantic Av-Barclays Ctr  [ad]<td>[4] and [2] [3] [D] [N] [Q] [R]</table>\r\nNote: No Weekend [5] service between Grand Central-42 St and Bowling Green.\r\n\r\nReminder: <a href=http://advisory.mtanyct.info/pdf_files/NightMap.pdf target=_blank>Late Night Service</a> at these [R] stations is provided by the [N].\r\n\r\n<table class=plannedworkTableStyle  border=1 cellspacing=1 cellpadding=5 rules=none frame=box><td>&nbsp;&nbsp;[ad]&nbsp;&nbsp;<td>This service change affects one or more ADA accessible stations. Please call 511 for help with planningyour trip. If you are deaf or hard of hearing, use your preferred relay service provider or the free 711 relay.&nbsp;&nbsp;</table>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n                \r\n              ", :active=>true}
