{:name=>"ACE", :status=>"DELAYS", :date=>"02/22/2015 12:41PM", :text=>"\r\n                    <span class=\"TitleDelay\">Delays</span>\r\n                    <span class=\"DateStyle\">\r\n                    &nbsp;Posted:&nbsp;02/22/2015&nbsp;12:41PM\r\n                    </span>\r\n                  <P>Due to track maintenance between<STRONG> Queens Plz</STRONG> and <STRONG>Forest Hills-71 Av</STRONG>, [E], [F] and [R] trains are running with delays in both directions.</P>\r\n<P>Allow additional travel time.</P>\r\n                \r\n              \r\n                    <span class=\"TitlePlannedWork\" >Planned Work</span>\r\n                    \r\n                  <a class=\"plannedWorkDetailLink\" onclick=ShowHide(89897);>\r\n[E] Jamaica Center-bound trains run local from Roosevelt Av to 71 Av\r\n</a><div id= 89897 class=\"plannedWorkDetail\" >Weekend, 12:01 AM Sat to 5 AM Mon, Feb 21 - 23\r\n\r\nTrains stop at Elmhurst, Grand Avs, Woodhaven Blvd, 63 Dr and 67 Av.\r\n\r\n&#149; Please allow additional travel time.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n                \r\n              \r\n                    <span class=\"TitlePlannedWork\" >Planned Work</span>\r\n                    \r\n                  <a class=\"plannedWorkDetailLink\" onclick=ShowHide(89894);>\r\n[E] Jamaica Center-bound trains skip Spring St and 23 St\r\n</a><div id= 89894 class=\"plannedWorkDetail\" >Weekend, 11:45 PM Fri to 5 AM Mon, Feb 20 - 23\r\n\r\nFor service to these stations, take the [E] to W 4 St or 34 St and transfer to a\r\ndowntown [A] local, [C] or [E].\r\n\r\nFor service from these stations, take the [A] [C] or [E] to 14 St or Canal St\r\nand transfer to a Jamaica Center-bound [E].\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n                \r\n              \r\n                    <span class=\"TitlePlannedWork\" >Planned Work</span>\r\n                    \r\n                  <a class=\"plannedWorkDetailLink\" onclick=ShowHide(90024);>\r\n[C] 168 St-bound trains run via the [F] from Jay St-MetroTech to 34 St-Herald Sq, <br clear=left>then via the [D] to 59 St-Columbus Circle\r\n</a><div id= 90024 class=\"plannedWorkDetail\" ><a href=http://advisory.mtanyct.info/pdf_files/ServiceGuide.pdf target=_blank>Weekend</a>, Saturday and Sunday, Feb 21 - 22\r\n\r\nNo 168 St-bound service at High, Fulton, Chambers, Canal, Spring, 14, 23, 34, 42 and 50 Sts.\r\n\r\nTravel Alternatives\r\n\r\nFor High, Fulton, Chambers, Canal 14, 34, and 42 Sts, take the [A] via transfer at \r\nJay St-MetroTech or 59 St-Columbus Circle.\r\n\r\nFor service to Spring St, take the [C] to W 4 St and transfer to a downtown [C] or [E].\r\n\r\nFor service from this station*, take the [C] or [E] to Canal St and transfer to an uptown [A] \r\nto 59 St-Columbus Circle where [C] service is available.\r\n\r\nFor service to 23 St, take the [C] to the 7 Av [D] [E] Station and transfer to a downtown [E].\r\n\r\nFor service from this station*, take the [C] or [E] to 14 St and transfer to an uptown [A] \r\nto 59 St where [C] service is available.\r\n\r\nFor 50 St, take the [E]. Transfer between trains at W 4 St or 7 Av. \r\n\r\n*This detour has taken into account additional planned service changes.\r\n\r\nAlternate travel note:\r\nFor 14, 23, 34, 42 and 50 Sts, use nearby [F] stations on 6 Av instead.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n                \r\n              \r\n                    <span class=\"TitlePlannedWork\" >Planned Work</span>\r\n                    \r\n                  <a class=\"plannedWorkDetailLink\" onclick=ShowHide(89985);>\r\n[A] No trains between Rockaway Blvd and Lefferts Blvd<br clear=left>[A] Howard Beach/Far Rockaway-bound trains skip 88 St \r\n</a><div id= 89985 class=\"plannedWorkDetail\" >[SB] Free shuttle buses provide alternate service\r\nWeekend, 11:45 PM Fri to 5 AM Mon, Feb 20 - 23\r\n\r\n[A] service operates between 207 St and Howard Beach-JFK Airport/Mott Av.\r\n\r\n[SB] buses make all stops between 80 St and Lefferts Blvd.\r\n\r\n&#149; Transfer between trains and buses at 80 St.\r\n\r\n<a style=\"cursor:pointer; text-decoration:underline;\" onclick=ShowHide(899850);>Show Shuttle Bus Stops</a><div id=\"899850\"; style=\"display:none;\"><table class=plannedworkTableStyle  border=1 cellspacing=1 cellpadding=3 rules=rows frame=hsides><tr bgcolor=FAF8CC><td>Station<td>Shuttle Bus Stop<tr><td>80 St  [A]<td>Liberty Av at 80 St<tr><td>88 St  [A] (Inwood-bound only)<td>Liberty Av at 88 St<tr><td rowspan=2>Rockaway Blvd&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;[A] (Inwood-bound only)<td>93 St at Liberty Av (to Lefferts Blvd)<tr><td>Liberty Av at 93 St (to 80 St)<tr><td>104 St<td>Liberty Av at 104 St<tr><td>111 St<td>Liberty Av at 111 St<tr><td>Lefferts Blvd<td>Lefferts Blvd at Liberty Av</table></div>\r\nNote: The Ozone Park/Far Rockaway-bound platform at Rockaway Blvd is closed for renovation. \r\n\r\nAlternate travel note:\r\nFor service to 88 St and Rockaway Blvd, take the [A] to Aqueduct-North Conduit Av\r\nand transfer to an Inwood-bound [A].\r\nFor service toward the Rockaways from these stations, take the [A] to 80 St\r\nand transfer to a Howard Beach/Far Rockaway-bound [A].\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n                \r\n              ", :active=>true}
